    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Sadly, the Solidity language does not let us remove a function from a contract's interface, so the best we can do is revert when `rate` is called on that particular crowdsale. The alternative would be to manually expose `rate` in all child crowdsales but that one, but I fear that would be too cumbersome and not worth the effort.",
